             was indicted for <rs id="t18220220-126-off680" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220220-126-off680" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220220-126-off680" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220220-126-cd681" type="crimeDate">15th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-126-off680 t18220220-126-cd681"></join>, one great coat, value 4 s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18220220-126-victim1235" type="victimName">
                     Manuel 
                     Reveiro
                  <interp inst="t18220220-126-victim1235" type="surname" value="Reveiro"></interp>
