                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-126-defend1233 t18220220-126-punish685"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs> and Discharged.</p>
               <p>Middlesex Jury, (half foreign,) before W. Arabin, Esq.</p>
